Package calculator

Class StandardCalc

java.lang.Object
calculator.StandardCalc
public class StandardCalc
extends Object
Class implements Calculator to evaluate Infix string expressions. Evaluating a Infix expression in StandardCalc will convert it to a RevPolishCalc where the actual calculation will take place.
Author:
David Kidd
See Also:
Inspiration for the infix to postfix conversion.
